<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">首1平方法，是指求十几的数的平方，可用100加上个位数的平方，再加上个位数的20倍，此数就是所求的平方数，可利用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(10+a)(10+a)=100+a×a+20a</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中这个数的个位数为a。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">17×17=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 17×17</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100+7×7+20×7</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100+49+140</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=149+140</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=289</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>